    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You rapidly spit out a small fireball, which deals 2d6 fire damage (Reflex negates). If a creature is hit for at least 15 fire damage by a single use of this technique, it must make a second Reflex save to avoid catching on fire.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to create an additional fireball (up to 1 per 2 levels total), which may target the same creature or square, or a different one. Spend 1 Chakra per fireball to increase the damage by 1d6.<br><br>You must empower all fireballs equally, and any single creature cannot be targeted by more than 1d6 per level worth of fireballs.</p>\n\n",
